Given k, find the geometric sum i.e.

1 + 1/2 + 1/4 + 1/8 + ... + 1/(2^k) 
Note :
using recursion.
Detailed explanation ( Input/output format, Notes, Images )
Constraints :
0 <= k <= 1000
Sample Input 1 :
3
Sample Output 1 :
1.87500
Sample Input 2 :
4
Sample Output 2 :
1.93750
Explanation for Sample Input 1:
1+ 1/(2^1) + 1/(2^2) + 1/(2^3) = 1.87500

//code...............

#include<cmath>
double geometricSum(int k) {
    // Write your code here
    if(k==0){
        return 1;
    }
    double cal=1/(pow(2,k));
    double smallSum= cal+geometricSum(k-1);

    return smallSum;

}


